arStrings.szText: Theya stole them. Pinned them on some necklace she wears, but takes it with her everywhere, makes me watch. I wonder if my suffering aids her?
lude, drunk, or a madman. shouts at everyone
Ah yeah, I can see through those eyes just as you can see me now, but what I see is painful. So much pain, so much death. I want my damned eyes back!
